<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="remark-v">remark <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'mɑːrk/    美 /rɪ'mɑːrk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 谈论；评论：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher <strong>remarked that</strong> the article was well written. 
老师评论说那篇文章写得很好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It would be rude to <strong>remark on / upon</strong> other’s appearance. 
对他人的相貌品头论足是不礼貌的。</p></div></div>